query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(l o p s d) */ select sum(l.l_revenue),
d.d_year,
p.p_brand1
from part AS p
inner join lineitem AS l
on l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey AND p.p_category = 'MFGR#12'
inner join orders AS o
on l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
inner join supplier AS s
on l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey AND s.s_region = 'AMERICA'
inner join date AS d
on o.o_orderdate = d.d_datekey group by d.d_year, p.p_brand1 order by d.d_year, p.p_brand1;
